songs.title: Curious (Sweater Beats Remix)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
I'm just curious
I'm just curious

[Verse 1]
I need a drink, whiskey ain't my thing
But shit is all good
I can handle things like I wish that you would
You've been out of reach, could you explain?
I think that you should
What you been up to?
Who's been loving you good?

[Pre-Chorus]
I'm just on the floor, I'm like a model
Been looking through the texts and all the photos
But don't you worry, I can handle it
No, don't you worry, I can handle it

[Chorus]
I'm just curious (I'm, I'm, I'm...)
I'm just curious (I'm, I'm, I'm...)
I'm just curious (I'm, I'm, I'm...)
I'm just curious (I'm, I'm, I'm...)

[Verse 2]
Calling me up, so late at night
Are we just friends?
You say you wanted me, but you're sleeping with him
You think of me, I'm what you see
When you look at the sky
I don't believe you
You ain't been loving me right, yeah

[Pre-Chorus]
I'm just on the floor, I'm like a model, yeah
Been looking through the texts and all the photos
But don't you worry I can handle it
No, don't you worry I can handle it

[Chorus]
I'm just curious (I'm, I'm, I'm...)
I'm just curious (I'm, I'm, I'm...)
I'm just curious (I'm, I'm, I'm...)
I'm just curious

[Bridge]
Touch ya, touch ya, touch ya, touch ya, touch ya
If you let him touch ya, touch ya, touch ya, touch ya
You let used to, used to, used to, used to, used to
Used to, used to, used to, used to, used to
Touch ya, touch ya, touch ya, touch ya, touch ya
If you let him touch ya, touch ya, touch ya, touch ya
You let used to, used to, used to, used to, used to
Used to, used to, used to, used to, used to

[Chorus 2]
(I'm just, I'm just)
I'm just curious
I'm just curious
I'm just, I'm just curious
